type.name: org.gradle.api.java.archives.ManifestMergeDetails
type.description: Details of a value being merged from two different manifests.

method.name: getKey
method.description: Returns the key that is to be merged.

method.name: setValue
method.description:
Set's the value for the key of the manifest after the merge takes place.
param:value

method.name: getValue
method.description: Returns the value for the key of the manifest after the merge takes place. By default this is the value of the source for the merge.

method.name: getSection
method.description: Returns the section this merge details belongs to.

method.name: getBaseValue
method.description: Returns the value for the key of the manifest that is the target of the merge.

method.name: getMergeValue
method.description: Returns the value for the key of the manifest that is the source for the merge.

method.name: exclude
method.description: Excludes this key from being in the manifest after the merge.

property.name: mergeValue
property.description: Returns the value for the key of the manifest that is the source for the merge.

property.name: key
property.description: Returns the key that is to be merged.

property.name: baseValue
property.description: Returns the value for the key of the manifest that is the target of the merge.

property.name: value
property.description: Returns the value for the key of the manifest after the merge takes place. By default this is the value of the source for the merge.

property.name: section
property.description: Returns the section this merge details belongs to.
